p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Return the closest parent context of the given type
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
The returned context is the closest parent which match the given `model type`. The `model type` must be a tag, or it can be one of the following utility name:

v

tag of the "type" of context that you are looking for. You can also provide the value named value such as:

- `parent` : return the closest context in the composition tree. From a lambda (iternator for exemple), it will return the context of the brick in which the lambda is attached.
- `application` : return the context of the running Application
- `screen` : in UI app, return the context of the running screen
